s. This was the name of the mother of John the Baptist (Luke 1:60). Etymologically, the name means ‘God is my oath’, and is therefore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth was born about 1252, in Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with William."},"et":{"ABT 1252–":"umbes 1252–Surnud","1250–1330":"1250–1330","1293–1383":"1293–1383","1252–Female":"1252–Surnud","ABT 1293":"umbes 1293","ABT 1252":"umbes 1252","7 Jul 1932":"7. juuli 1932","1330":"1330","1252":"1252","1383":"1383","1250":"1250","1293":"1293","2 Jul 1932":"2. juuli 1932","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Gawthorpe, Yorkshire, England":"Gawthorpe, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"ABT 1252–":"noin 1252–Kuollut","1250–1330":"1250–1330","1293–1383":"1293–1383","1252–Female":"1252–Kuollut","ABT 1293":"noin 1293","ABT 1252":"noin 1252","7 Jul 1932":"7. heinäkuuta 1932","1330":"1330","1252":"1252","1383":"1383","1250":"1250","1293":"1293","2 Jul 1932":"2. heinäkuuta 1932","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Gawthorpe, Yorkshire, England":"Gawthorpe, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"ABT 1252–":"environ 1252–Décédée","1250–1330":"1250–1330","1293–1383":"1293–1383","1252–Female":"1252–Décédée","ABT 1293":"environ 1293","ABT 1252":"environ 1252","7 Jul 1932":"7 juillet 1932","1330":"1330","1252":"1252","1383":"1383","1250":"1250","1293":"1293","2 Jul 1932":"2 juillet 1932","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Gawthorpe, Yorkshire, England":"Gawthorpe, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth est née environ 1252, à Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec William."},"de":{"ABT 1252–":"um 1252–Verstorben","1250–1330":"1250–1330","1293–1383":"1